 "name": "RPlog_Rescued_In_Transit",
 "title": "Rescued in Transit",
 "summary": "Aboard the Imperial prisoner transport Justice, Captain Ryder and the baton-swinging Sergeant Tycho oversee captives -- among them the stirring Wolf -- hung and electrocuted in the holding compartment. Unbeknownst to the crew, the black-clad Tritus and his band, including a violence-hungry human woman, lie in wait on the barren world of Caluula along the transport's route. As the ship comes into range, Tritus fires a rocket to bring it down, springing a deadly ambush to free the prisoners in transit. The log opens a brutal rescue operation against an Imperial prison ship.",
